data.title: Fall of 2022 Dean’s List
data.meta_description: The Clemson University Dean’s List is awarded to those who achieve a 3.5-grade point average on a minimum of 12 semester hours, exclusive of Pass/No Pass coursework.
data.text:
Clemson News

Share:

The Clemson University Dean’s List is one of the most prestigious honors a student can earn. It is awarded to those who achieve a 3.5-grade point average on a minimum of 12 semester hours, exclusive of Pass/No Pass coursework.

The complete Fall of 2022 Dean’s List is listed below in alphabetical order based on last name.

Every individual awarded deserves to be celebrated, and we invite you to create a shareable image to commemorate this milestone by visiting the University’s President’s and Dean’s List website. There, you will be able to type in a student’s name to create a custom badge to save, send or share.
